                              ^^^                                                                                       
                       was a major barrier to fighting poverty. War on Want's John Hilary said: "Compassionate rhetoric 
                                                                                                                        
                      cannot disguise the reality of the government's neo-liberal policies. "As long as Mr Blair and Mr 
                                      ^^^            ^^^                                                                
                      Brown continue to push free trade and privatisation on developing countries, more and more people 
                                                                                                                        
